{"tid":2318753,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一生人都無去過日本是否失敗","createTime":"2020-12-09T14:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T20:11:49.000Z","uid":112551,"like":9,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"49aaf48159cb69c3d55347e1fcf562a2d773de18","tid":2318753,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:43:26.000Z","msg":"自細睇唔少日本動漫電視節目，又成日食日本食物，又成日去donki 一田⋯⋯<br />\n無學日文都識少少日文⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n身份此同開始出咗問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係香港人但生活離不開日本。<br />\n但一生人都無去過日本是否失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚大學畢業後返工無時間去旅行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪真架？"},{"pid":"f1b73d17acba6aa18901ef194850618588461c26","tid":2318753,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"身份*認同"},{"pid":"797b522914030bc4a5e7d5ad8adfd5d5c0663093","tid":2318753,"uid":226355,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"49aaf48159cb69c3d55347e1fcf562a2d773de18","tid":2318753,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:43:26.000Z","msg":"自細睇唔少日本動漫電視節目，又成日食日本食物，又成日去donki 一田⋯⋯<br />\n無學日文都識少少日文⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n身份此同開始出咗問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係香港人但生活離不開日本。<br />\n但一生人都無去過日本是否失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚大學畢業後返工無時間去旅行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪真架？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:43:24.000Z","msg":"無去過日本點會係失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主諗野正面啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畢業之後有機會咪去日本玩下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由細到大都好鍾意日本<br />\n屋企人又從事日本產品銷售既生意<br />\n生活一直都同日本連繫住<br />\n到最後自己去左日本定居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路係自己行出黎，加油！"},{"pid":"df66bb2f